description: Represents a ropersontic kiss between two people with medium-dark to dark skin tones, conveying affection and love.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this intimate emoji depicts two individuals sharing a tender kiss, rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and soft, rounded edges.  The medium-dark and dark skin tones are presented with subtle gradients, reflecting realistic lighting and conveying a deep sense of affection and romantic connection.  It's a beautiful representation of love and partnership, perfect for expressing romantic feelings or celebrating relationships on Apple devices.
